            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Quen mihtotiah quehce achi cuahuitonih huan yehyectizn quen necih, mocuamalacachoah huan mooholinia ica ininicxi huan inintlacayo, nochipa mochihua ica tlatzotzontli.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
